<subSubSection lastPageId="380" lastPageNumber="381" pageId="379" pageNumber="380" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="379" pageNumber="380">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph lastPageId="380" lastPageNumber="381" pageId="379" pageNumber="380">
The range of this western species extends from Vancouver Island (Lindroth 1963b: 323) to western Montana (Russell 1968: 53; Edwards 1975: 53), north 
<pageBreakToken pageId="380" pageNumber="381" start="start">to</pageBreakToken>
central British Columbia (Lindroth 1963b: 323), south to southern California (Hayward 1897: 79; Fall 1901a: 42; Moore 1937: 6). The record from &quot;New Mexico&quot; (Bousquet and Larochelle 1993: 136) is probably in error.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
